text: Sävsjö HK is a handball club in Sävsjö in Sweden. The club was established on 1 August 1978. The women's team won six Swedish national championship gold meals in a row between the 1993-1994 and the 1998-1999 seasons. During the 2002/2003 season the women's team was relegated from Elitserien. == References == ==Other websites== *official website Category:1978 establishments in Sweden Category:Handball clubs in Sweden
